{"tid":8210,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"不堪丈夫變態性癖 熟婦用剃鬚刀斬斷陽具","createTime":"2016-11-28T08:22:18.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T20:33:05.000Z","uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3e711460adf482425dca15481823c80cd44dd5e6","tid":8210,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T08:22:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20160129/640_9b70e2cea0bee94da7ed73b98182ef18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20160129%2F640_9b70e2cea0bee94da7ed73b98182ef18.jpg&h=05d67b0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬來西亞一名51歲人妻趁著丈夫熟睡剁下其陰莖，她昨天在庭上認罪。<br />\n馬來西亞《星報》報導，馬來西亞巴都基基（Batu Kikir）51歲婦人阿布杜拉（Fatimah Abdullah）本月20日凌晨約1時半，拿剃鬍子的刮刀割去44歲丈夫陽具。這是阿布杜拉第二段婚姻，她前段婚姻育有5子女。<br />\n阿布杜拉向警方表示，她受不了丈夫變態的性癖，才揮刀斬斷對方命根，兩人在2014年結婚。阿布杜拉昨天出庭時表情冷靜，她被控持械加重攻擊罪，案件將在下月22日宣判。法院昨裁定以5萬令吉交保（約4萬元台幣）。（余浚安／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"a5bdf3359b1cf7dd9f42595a937f0b67baded42a","tid":8210,"uid":2507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T08:22:37.000Z","msg":"好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef1eca5c46834f2c0cd345d369dbb61641784d10","tid":8210,"uid":4363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T08:24:31.000Z","msg":"條鳩要幾細先可以剃斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f53a10cce6da95bfe97002848abdc284d87f1d69","tid":8210,"uid":4156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T08:26:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條鳩要幾細先可以剃斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n剃刀呀？"},{"pid":"c8111ff416242ff69c9696e40c1021774b1dec98","tid":8210,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T08:38:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>條鳩要幾細先可以剃斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n剃刀呀？</blockquote><br />\n<br />